 <b>Cooperation program with Shahnoza-Fayz Clinic in Tashkent, Uzbekistan</b>
</p>
 An agreement of cooperation with the Shahnoza-Fayz Clinic was signed. We had to transfer our clinical protocols to the colleagues in Uzbekistan, achieve professional understanding, win trust of the Uzbek doctors and patients. We created a united approach to pre-treatment assessment and preparation for the IVF programs, established direct contacts between our specialists, introduced the procedure of referring patients “from doctor to doctor”. The cooperation has led to impressive results: of 588 patients from Uzbekistan who have had IVF treatment in the recent 5 years, the pregnancy rate is 62.4%, 381 babies were born, 16 women are pregnant (on October 15, 2019). In the group of patients under 30, the pregnancy rate is 72.7%.<br>
 <br>
 Our success in the joint program with the Uzbek colleagues shows how important is not only high qualification and extended experience of the specialists but also consistency and shared understanding of the treatment strategy at all stages starting from patients’ examination and their preparation for the treatment cycle to pregnancy management and childbirth.&nbsp;<br>
 <br>";s:15:"PREVIEW_PICTURE";a:6:{s:8:"ORIGINAL";s:33:"/upload/iblock/492/Group_3_1_.png";s:13:"webp_ORIGINAL";s:56:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/492/0_0_1_95/Group_3_1_.webp";s:7:"preview";s:33:"/upload/iblock/492/Group_3_1_.png";s:12:"webp_preview";s:60:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/492/160_160_1_95/Group_3_1_.webp";s:7:"history";s:33:"/upload/iblock/492/Group_3_1_.png";s:12:"webp_history";s:60:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/492/142_142_1_95/Group_3_1_.webp";}s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"79";s:19:"PROPERTY_YEAR_VALUE";s:4:"2008";s:22:"PROPERTY_YEAR_VALUE_ID";s:9:"51711:401";s:4:"SORT";s:3:"170";s:17:"PREVIEW_TEXT_TYPE";s:4:"html";}i:24571;a:9:{s:2:"ID";s:5:"24571";s:4:"NAME";s:105:"Involvement into launching ART Department at the Almazov Federal Center of Heart, Blood and Endocrinology";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:503:"<div class="history-card__title">
